[
  "Liu Ko-chen, also known as K.C. Liu, is chairman and CEO of industrial-automation-equipment and software supplier Advantech.",
  "Liu co-founded Advantech in 1983 at age 29 with two colleagues from HP Taiwan.",
  "Advantech also makes industrial computers; in recent years it has expanded to provide Internet-of-things intelligent systems and cloud solutions.",
  "Liu's wife, Mary Chang, holds a large stake in the company."
]